<BaseLayout 
  title="About Dr. Colin MacLeod ND" 
  description="Learn about Dr. Colin MacLeod, naturopathic doctor in Halifax, Nova Scotia. Professional background, treatment philosophy and approach to naturopathic medicine."
  focusKeyword="Dr Colin MacLeod naturopathic doctor Halifax"
