  <section class="bg-emerald-950 -mt-24 pt-48 pb-24 lg:pt-56 lg:pb-32">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">About Dr. Colin MacLeod ND</h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Dedicated to providing evidence-based naturopathic medicine with a focus on treating the root cause of illness and promoting optimal health.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main About Content -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        
        <!-- Profile Information -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-6">Professional Background</h2>
            
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Dr. Colin MacLeod is a licensed naturopathic doctor serving the Halifax, Nova Scotia community with a commitment to comprehensive, evidence-based natural healthcare. His practice combines the wisdom of traditional healing methods with modern scientific research to provide effective, individualized treatment plans.
            </p>

            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
              With extensive training in clinical nutrition, botanical medicine, acupuncture and regenerative injection therapies, Dr. MacLeod specializes in treating chronic pain conditions, fatigue, digestive disorders and helping patients achieve optimal wellness through natural approaches.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Education & Training</h3>
            <div class="bg-emerald-50/30 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8">
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-800 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Doctor of naturopathic medicine (ND) - Canadian College of Naturopathic Medicine</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
