                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Treatment Philosophy</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Dr. MacLeod's approach to healthcare is rooted in the fundamental naturopathic principles of treating the whole person, addressing root causes and supporting the body's inherent ability to heal itself. He believes in creating individualized treatment plans that combine the best of traditional wisdom with current scientific evidence.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-emerald-50 border-l-4 border-emerald-600 rounded-r-2xl p-6 mb-8">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-2">Core Treatment Principles</h4>
              <ul class="text-emerald-800 space-y-2">
                <li>• <strong>First, Do No Harm:</strong> Using gentle, non-invasive therapies whenever possible</li>
                <li>• <strong>Treat the Whole Person:</strong> Addressing physical, mental and emotional aspects of health</li>
                <li>• <strong>Identify Root Causes:</strong> Looking beyond symptoms to find underlying imbalances</li>
                <li>• <strong>Support Natural Healing:</strong> Enhancing the body's own healing mechanisms</li>
                <li>• <strong>Patient Education:</strong> Empowering patients with knowledge about their health</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
